content:
UI Text and Functionality Improvements in Privacy Center

We updated the user interface text in several places to improve the user experience. We also changed the behavior of two privacy policy filter operators.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

Review these changes:

* The "is before" operator was renamed to "is within the last". It captures records whose date field is within a specified number of days before the policy execution date.
* The "is after" operator was renamed to "is beyond the last". It captures records whose date field is beyond a specified number of days before the policy execution date.
* The "Number of Days" field was renamed to "Number of Days Relative to Policy Execution Date".
* The "Preview" field was renamed to "Summary".

Additionally, we added warnings for:

* Applying the Permanently delete records setting
* Canceling an in-progress job for a privacy policy
title: UI Text and Functionality Improvements in Privacy Center
